{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-309-integer-ladders","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 309: Nivoi za potpune brojeve","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U tipičnom problemu \"Presečne ljestvice\", dato nam je dužina $x$ i $y$ dve ljestvice oslonjene na suprotne zidove uske ravne ulice. Takođe nam je data visina $h$ iznad ulice gde ove dve ljestvice prelaze, a traži se širina ulice ($w$).</p>\n<img alt=\"ngazi x na y, zikivuka kwa urefu h, na kushikiliwa kwenye kuta zinazokabiliwa za mtaa wenye upana w\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/integer-ladders.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Ovde razmatramo samo slučajeve gde su sve varijable pozitivni ceo brojevi. Na primer, ako su $x = 70$, $y = 119$ i $h = 30$, možemo izračunati da je $w = 56$.</p>\n<p>Zaista, za cele vrednosti $x$, $y$, $h$ i $0 &#x3C; $x$ &#x3C; $y$ &#x3C; 200$, postoje samo pet skupova ($x$, $y$, $h$) koji formiraju celobrojna rešenja za $w$: (70, 119, 30), (74, 182, 21), (87, 105, 35), (100, 116, 35) i (119, 175, 40).</p>\n<p>Za cela brojačka vrednosti $x$, $y$, $h$ i $0 &#x3C; x &#x3C; y &#x3C; 1\\,000\\,000$, koliko je skupova $(x$, $y$, $h)$ koje čine celobrojna rešenja za $w$?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4a11000cf542c50ffb4","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301963,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-309-integer-ladders"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function integerLadders() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nintegerLadders();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>integerLadders()</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>210139</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(integerLadders(), 210139);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-301-to-400","dashedName":"problem-309-integer-ladders","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-310-nim-square","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-308-an-amazing-prime-generating-automaton","id":"5900f4a11000cf542c50ffb4","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-309-integer-ladders"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}